column5: Hey guys........headed up to Sioux Narrows Friday for a week.....couple of questions.....crawlers in beddings still ok?.......and how many cigars can you bring into Canada?......any fishing tips or reports for the area would be greatly apprectiated too.......thanks In advance......I'll post how we did when I get back......
You can still bring 50 cigars or 200 cigarettes.
Crawlers in paper bedding are okay, nothing organic!
You might want to look at this website. It will answer a lot of your questions.http://www.infonorth.net/
